FT  28 APR 93 / Ex-Bestwood chief sentenced
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MR TONY COLE, the former chairman and chief executive of the Bestwood Group,
yesterday received a two-year suspended jail sentence after admitting
misappropriating more than Pounds 700,000 from the company to finance his
personal share dealing.
He was also disqualified from being a company director for 10 years.
