FT  28 APR 93 / Lloyds Bank joins Switch scheme
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
LLOYDS BANK has joined the Switch debit card scheme to which the other large
high street banks already belong. The bank said yesterday it would offer to
process Switch debit transactions on behalf of retailers.
Lloyd's 'merchant acquiring' operation has until now only processed
Mastercard and Visa transactions including the Visa Delta debit card.
